{"data":{"wordpressPost":{"title":"Japan Trip 2015 Part 1: Osaka&#8230;?","content":"<html><head></head><body><p>\t\t\t\tGary and I had a later flight than the rest of the crew, so the original plan was for us to meet up with everyone a few hours later in Osaka. However, we ended up missing our flight to Tokyo for reasons completely beyond our control.</p>\n<p><!--more--></p>\n<p>We <em>may</em> have gotten into an intense Bomberman match on our 3DS&#x2019;s and missed our boarding call, but what really happened? Nobody knows.</p>\n<p><div class=\" gatsby-image-wrapper\" style=\"position:relative;overflow:hidden;max-width:100%;width:951px\" data-reactroot><div style=\"width:100%;padding-bottom:107.6797385620915%\"></div><img src=\"data:image/jpeg;base64,\" alt style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center;opacity:1;transition-delay:500ms\"><picture><img sizes=\"(max-width: 951px) 100vw, 951px\" srcset=\"/static/4d0ff203c92b7575aad323429fceb3ff/88b85/IMG_4025.jpg 238w,\n/static/4d0ff203c92b7575aad323429fceb3ff/5c586/IMG_4025.jpg 476w,\n/static/4d0ff203c92b7575aad323429fceb3ff/961df/IMG_4025.jpg 951w,\n/static/4d0ff203c92b7575aad323429fceb3ff/05429/IMG_4025.jpg 1224w\" src=\"/static/4d0ff203c92b7575aad323429fceb3ff/961df/IMG_4025.jpg\" alt style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center;opacity:1;transition:opacity 500ms\"></picture><noscript><picture><img sizes=\"(max-width: 951px) 100vw, 951px\" srcset=\"/static/4d0ff203c92b7575aad323429fceb3ff/88b85/IMG_4025.jpg 238w,\n/static/4d0ff203c92b7575aad323429fceb3ff/5c586/IMG_4025.jpg 476w,\n/static/4d0ff203c92b7575aad323429fceb3ff/961df/IMG_4025.jpg 951w,\n/static/4d0ff203c92b7575aad323429fceb3ff/05429/IMG_4025.jpg 1224w\" src=\"/static/4d0ff203c92b7575aad323429fceb3ff/961df/IMG_4025.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;opacity:1;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center\"/></picture></noscript></div></p>\n<div class=\"sub\">MISSIN FLIGHTS LOL</div>\n<p>So, our first day consisted of missing a flight, getting a nice Aeroplan agent to rebook a flight for us, missing another flight in LA (for legit reasons this time &#x2013; plane crapped out), and getting a paid-for hotel room. The next morning we had a ballin steak&#x2019;n&#x2019;eggs breakfast courtesy of Air Canada and flew out to Osaka.</p>\n<p>Excellent start to the trip!</p>\n<h2>Takeaways:</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Don&#x2019;t get into a heated Bomberman sesh right before boarding a flight.</li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<p><a href=\"/japan-trip-2015/\">&#x2190; Back to Japan Trip 2015 index</a>\t\t</p>\n</body></html>","wordpress_id":4232},"allWordpressWpComments":{"edges":[{"node":{"content":"<p>ahahaha. I done goofed bahd! It all turned out alright though ðŸ™‚</p>\n","author_name":"tetchi","date":"February 22nd, 2016"}},{"node":{"content":"<p>Can&#8217;t believe you missed your flight bahd! ðŸ˜€</p>\n","author_name":"iamkeir","date":"February 22nd, 2016"}}]}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"slug":"japan-trip-2015-part-1-osaka","wordpressId":4232,"newerPostSlug":"japan-trip-2015-part-2-kyoto","olderPostSlug":"japan-trip-2015"}}